(Half a month later)

16
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:14,400
Extra! Extra!

17
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,959
Master Liu's comeback play!

18
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:17,879
Ruyi Theater's new play
takes the city by storm.

19
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,200
Based on a true story.

20
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,799
A fresh adaptation of The Encounter.

21
00:01:21,159 --> 00:01:22,280
Extra! Extra!

22
