27
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:43,760
Is it really that good?

28
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,840
Exactly!

29
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,079
It's amazing.

30
00:01:46,079 --> 00:01:47,799
Absolutely breathtaking.

31
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:50,079
Master Liu and Miss Shen
make a perfect duo

32
00:01:50,079 --> 00:01:51,000
and dazzle the venue.

33
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,120
What's even more remarkable is

34
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,120
the gimmick
of being based on a true story.

35
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:57,040
It makes people
can't help but speculate.

36
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:57,920
A true story?

37
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,200
Who?

38
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,239
You don't know?

39
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:01,359
Jin Ping, the Wangs' live-in son-in-law.

40
00:02:01,359 --> 00:02:02,760
I heard recently

41
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,400
the Wangs took him
to Mr. Guan's private gathering.

42
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,560
They ran into his ex-fiancée,

43
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:09,639
