funding his eight-year study abroad.

44
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:11,319
The theater folks were furious

45
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,639
and beat him and threw him out.

46
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:14,039
It serves him right.

47
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,080
A heartless scoundrel.

48
00:02:18,638 --> 00:02:19,840
(Shen Muling, Tonight's star)

49
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:21,960
Senior,

50
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,639
I've delivered your message

51
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:24,520
for Commander Xu.

52
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,599
Senior,

53
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:33,960
today is Mr. Guan's private gathering.

54
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,639
Would it be improper to invite

55
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,240
Commander Xu abruptly?

56
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:40,199
You'll know soon.

57
00:02:42,719 --> 00:02:43,559
Don't overthink it.

58
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,520
The audience is waiting.

59
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,439
I'll do your makeup today.

60
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,840
Make way.

61
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,599
