Let me go!

66
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,639
Today I'll smash this troupe!

67
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,120
Honey!

68
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,159
Calm down.

69
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:03,240
