72
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,560
How can I stay calm!

73
00:03:07,319 --> 00:03:08,439
If it weren't for you...

74
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,280
Forget it.

75
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,120
Let me go!

76
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:11,800
Honey.

77
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,640
Honey!

78
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:17,719
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

79
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:19,000
Who dares to applaud?

80
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:24,920
Honey.

81
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,520
Shen Muling!

82
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:30,840
What?

83
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,680
Brave enough to sing the opera,

84
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,479
