85
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,560
Mrs. Jin.

86
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,680
I was looking for you.

87
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,199
Someone here

88
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,520
has something to tell you.

89
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:50,639
