90
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,919
Perfect.

91
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:03,560
I knew

92
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,960
it was you again, little hussy!

93
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,680
I'll tear you apart today!

94
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,800
Calm down, Madam.

95
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,199
That day I did recognize Mr. Jin.

96
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:12,039
That's true.

97
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,919
I found him becoming

98
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:15,960
the Wang family's son-in-law
behind my back.

99
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,000
So I despised him

100
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,080
and hated him.

101
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,560
That's also true.

102
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:23,279
But I wasn't the one pestering him.

103
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,480
He was the one pestering me.

104
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:26,720
You...

105
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,560
You're slandering me!

106
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,040
Back in the village,

107
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:32,000
I repeatedly asked
to break off our engagement.

108
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:34,759
You were the one clinging to me.

109
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:36,240
