Commander Xu.

294
00:12:12,279 --> 00:12:13,119
You're here.

295
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,440
Duty delayed me.

296
00:12:14,799 --> 00:12:15,639
Am I late?

297
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:16,759
No.

298
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,560
What are you doing?

299
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:23,239
Are you okay?

300
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,360
They're fighting.

301
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,360
Are you in trouble?

302
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,440
Shen Muling,

303
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:32,759
it's a lie, right?

304
00:12:35,559 --> 00:12:36,399
Mr. Guan,

305
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:39,279
everything between us
has just been an act.

306
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:40,960
Since it's an act,

307
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,559
none of it was real.

308
00:12:43,799 --> 00:12:44,639
Just blame yourself

309
00:12:45,279 --> 00:12:46,720
for getting too invested.

310
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:52,639
Let's go.

311
00:12:57,639 --> 00:12:59,200
So it really is the Commander!

312
00:13:24,750 --> 00:13:27,998
♪Fire devours tears♪

313
00:13:28,462 --> 00:13:31,559
♪Cries fade in the smoke♪

314
00:13:32,494 --> 00:13:35,971
♪Storms gather♪

315
00:13:36,046 --> 00:13:39,646
♪Glory falls like ashes♪

316
00:13:40,238 --> 00:13:43,549
♪Sleeves flutter♪

317
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:47,213
♪You sing of love and hate
on high stage♪

318
00:13:47,982 --> 00:13:51,245
♪Yearning brings only sorrow♪

319
00:13:51,598 --> 00:13:55,768
♪But in your eyes, I found resolve♪

320
00:13:57,550 --> 00:14:01,315
♪After one final song of parting♪

321
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:05,095
♪We'll meet again only through tears♪

322
00:14:05,294 --> 00:14:08,987
♪Silently, pain blossoms♪

323
00:14:09,166 --> 00:14:12,787
♪In the flames, we embrace♪

324
00:14:13,230 --> 00:14:16,879
♪After one last song of joy and grief♪

325
00:14:16,974 --> 00:14:20,544
♪Lovers sigh under the endless moon♪

326
00:14:20,686 --> 00:14:24,230
♪Your face, like a mirage♪

327
00:14:24,526 --> 00:14:31,490
♪Becomes clear again in the ruins♪
